programming or engineering.

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:58.860
I think if Google
was not as creative

00:02:58.860 --> 00:03:01.800
when they were doing the
algorithms back then,

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:03.850
it would not be
what it is today.

00:03:03.850 --> 00:03:07.710
So a lot of people
would say, yeah,

00:03:07.710 --> 00:03:08.940
I'm not the creative type.

00:03:08.940 --> 00:03:09.450
No.

00:03:09.450 --> 00:03:10.360
We all are.

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:14.100
We just have to
find that one edge.

00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:17.700
We have to find how we can
synergize and capitalize

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:21.030
on that on our own strengths.

00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:24.040
