But what I'm saying is--

00:45:42.830 --> 00:45:45.080
NICHOLAS TSE: Did you guys
open like a new department?

00:45:46.315 --> 00:45:49.870
JAMES TAO: Like, I know you
help a lot of young people.

00:45:49.870 --> 00:45:53.200
But you're also a young
person yourself, right?

00:45:53.200 --> 00:45:55.440
So when you do come across--

00:45:55.440 --> 00:45:56.690
NICHOLAS TSE: Same generation.

00:45:56.690 --> 00:45:57.607
JAMES TAO: Yeah, yeah.

00:45:57.607 --> 00:45:58.510
Same generation.

00:45:58.510 --> 00:46:02.560
When you do come across
difficult decisions and stuff,

00:46:02.560 --> 00:46:04.120
do you just solely--

00:46:04.120 --> 00:46:06.773
you're comfortable relying
on yourself and just

00:46:06.773 --> 00:46:07.690
thinking that through?

