00:46:09.815 --> 00:46:14.110
because I'm facing similar kind
of situations for my career.

00:46:17.330 --> 00:46:19.520
NICHOLAS TSE: I've
always been able to--

00:46:19.520 --> 00:46:21.650
I've always been able
to gradually work out

00:46:21.650 --> 00:46:23.210
the problems in my life.

00:46:23.210 --> 00:46:24.440
So yeah.

