that I work on,
sometimes it's music.

00:46:32.050 --> 00:46:33.410
Sometimes it's film.

00:46:33.410 --> 00:46:34.850
Sometimes it's business.

00:46:34.850 --> 00:46:37.020
Sometimes it's
kind of a bit tech.

00:46:37.020 --> 00:46:38.900
So there's not really
that one person I

00:46:38.900 --> 00:46:42.945
can talk to regarding
all the different fields.

