00:46:48.300 --> 00:46:48.690
NICHOLAS TSE: Thank you.

00:46:48.690 --> 00:46:49.220
Thank you.

00:46:49.220 --> 00:46:50.630
JAMES TAO: Some people
actually flew in.

00:46:50.630 --> 00:46:50.900
NICHOLAS TSE: Really?

00:46:50.900 --> 00:46:51.970
AUDIENCE: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:46:51.970 --> 00:46:52.440
NICHOLAS TSE: Thank you.

00:46:52.440 --> 00:46:52.940
Thank you.

00:46:52.940 --> 00:46:56.420
AUDIENCE: So I'm curious to
know what are the messages

00:46:56.420 --> 00:46:59.435
or expectation or
impact that you expect

00:46:59.435 --> 00:47:03.330
to bring through your music,
your art, or entire passion to

00:47:03.330 --> 00:47:04.190
[INAUDIBLE]?

00:47:04.190 --> 00:47:07.730
NICHOLAS TSE: Through music,
through movies, of course.

00:47:07.730 --> 00:47:09.430
Mainly it's entertainment.

00:47:09.430 --> 00:47:13.435
And music, I could say,
I hope it brings more--

00:47:16.770 --> 00:47:19.740
I hope my music can also
stimulate or console you

00:47:19.740 --> 00:47:21.250
in your everyday life.

00:47:21.250 --> 00:47:23.340
But in terms of
a deeper message,

00:47:23.340 --> 00:47:25.650
we're trying to do that
through the "Chef Nic" show.

00:47:25.650 --> 00:47:29.580
Because as like what I was
saying about we don't share

00:47:29.580 --> 00:47:35.440
correctly or how we are missing
the essence of eating together,

00:47:35.440 --> 00:47:38.895
I really, really learned a
lot through the kitchen--

00:47:38.895 --> 00:47:41.520
the time management
stuff, the sharing part.

00:47:41.520 --> 00:47:45.480
It has changed my
personality immensely.

00:47:45.480 --> 00:47:48.960
I was a really different person
before I started cooking.

00:47:48.960 --> 00:47:54.040
And I think especially
in this day and age

00:47:54.040 --> 00:48:04.250
we hope to promote a lot
more activities or wilderness

00:48:04.250 --> 00:48:06.680
wildlife activities,
or stuff that you

00:48:06.680 --> 00:48:11.360
could do apart from just looking
at the phone or the computer.

00:48:11.360 --> 00:48:16.000
I think that's a very, very
important part of life.

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:18.560
AUDIENCE: I've got a question
more about your film career.

00:48:18.560 --> 00:48:20.740
So I just wanted to
know moving forward--

00:48:20.740 --> 00:48:23.680
so first of all, congratulations
on the Best Actor award.

00:48:23.680 --> 00:48:25.790
Moving forward for your
future film projects,

00:48:25.790 --> 00:48:28.310
are you going to be pursuing
more action-driven movies

00:48:28.310 --> 00:48:29.480
like "Police Story"?

00:48:29.480 --> 00:48:33.575
Or are you going to go for more
controversial or dramatic roles

00:48:33.575 --> 00:48:36.560
that kind of further challenge
your acting abilities?

00:48:36.560 --> 00:48:38.730
NICHOLAS TSE: I don't
really have a preference.

00:48:38.730 --> 00:48:44.780
I think that I am--

00:48:44.780 --> 00:48:51.570
sometimes you need a bit of
luck when you're given a script.

00:48:51.570 --> 00:48:53.100
The cast has got to be right.

00:48:53.100 --> 00:48:55.018
The story has to be right.

00:48:55.018 --> 00:48:56.310
The whole crew has to be right.

00:48:56.310 --> 00:48:58.110
The timing has to be right.

00:48:58.110 --> 00:49:00.070
We always say that in
the movie industry.

00:49:00.070 --> 00:49:03.870
Each movie has its
own journey, really.

00:49:03.870 --> 00:49:08.280
All you could do is do your
best when it is handed to you.

00:49:08.280 --> 00:49:10.500
But I do think there
is one that I'm

00:49:10.500 --> 00:49:13.420
planning on in a few months.

00:49:13.420 --> 00:49:14.700
It is action packed.

00:49:14.700 --> 00:49:21.210
I do think Hong Kong has to find
its roots some way, somehow.

00:49:21.210 --> 00:49:25.170
And to me, Hong Kong movie
is about Hong Kong action.

00:49:25.170 --> 00:49:29.190
It has never really been
about Hong Kong drama.

00:49:29.190 --> 00:49:33.350
So it's going to be tough.

00:49:33.350 --> 00:49:35.290
But I think, yes,
I'm going to have

00:49:35.290 --> 00:49:37.860
to dig down and fight again.

00:49:37.860 --> 00:49:40.990
And maybe jump off
